* Iron Raptor stopped just before entering the controle room when she 
recieved Quatro's transmission, glancing at Iris and then thinking for a sec 
before she replied.
If this bot was a bounty hunter then wasn't there the chance that he could 
turn on them too?
She knew that she hadn't trusted anyone for the longest of times now but 
being careful saved necks, even though her attetude might break them from 
time to time.
She activated her comm link and replied.*

" You might be a help, but I need to meet you before I even consider 
anything. I'll be in the controle room of the CF, I'll have an escotr 
waiting at the front doors when you arrive, they'll show you the way."

* That was all she was going to do at the moment, Iris giving her an annoyed 
look from under her helm.
Iron was too nice sometimes, if you wanted to call this nice.
Iron Raptor entered into the controle room, wondering who could be Quatro's 
escorts.
There was Prowl but he was making up the plan with Epyon. So niether were 
available...though...maybe she only needed one......
Iron Looked at Iris, she only nodding before leaving the room and leaving IR 
to think or do whatever she needed to.
Iron Raptor growled and turned back towards the controle room, wondering 
where in the inferno was Histeria when she'd asked for her.*

" Histeria?!"

* She called, wondering if the fembot was hidden under some console out of 
site working on something or if she was even in the room.*
